highlights.text: Olivia Rodrigo has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “good 4 u” is the highest at #5.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 238 weeks straight.
“Raataan Lambiyan (From "Shershaah")” by Tanishk Bagchi, Jubin Nautiyal, and Asees Kaur is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 98 spots at #63.
“Visiting Hours” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #30.
